<item>
            <title>[LU-15998] PCC: sanity-pcc/3b failed with copytool setup with multiple agents</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15998</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On both master and b_es6_0, sanity-pcc/3b failed with the following errors:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b0da45b1-0172-47de-b993-f334b5882134&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b0da45b1-0172-47de-b993-f334b5882134&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Starting copytool &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;agt2&apos;&lt;/span&gt; on &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;trevis-82vm3&apos;&lt;/span&gt; with cmdline &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;lhsmtool_posix --hsm-root=/tmp/arc1/sanity-pcc.test_3b/ --archive-format=v1 --daemon --pid-file=/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;/run/lhsmtool_posix.pid --archive 2  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/mnt/lustre&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
CMD: trevis-82vm3 lhsmtool_posix --hsm-root=/tmp/arc1/sanity-pcc.test_3b/ --archive-format=v1 --daemon --pid-file=/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;/run/lhsmtool_posix.pid --archive 2  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/mnt/lustre&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt; /dev/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/autotest/autotest-2/2022-07-07/lustre-reviews_custom_88325_1_101_9c7e9e43-202a-4c03-aeca-58a994a43ae9&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//sanity-pcc.test_3b.copytool2_log.trevis-82vm3.log&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
&lt;/span&gt;pdsh@trevis-82vm1: trevis-82vm3: ssh exited with exit code 254
 sanity-pcc test_3b: @@@@@@ FAIL: Failed to start copytool agt2 on &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;trevis-82vm3&apos;&lt;/span&gt; 
  Trace dump:
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6522:error()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:10526:copytool()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-pcc.sh:681:test_3b()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6857:run_one()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6904:run_one_logged()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:6745:run_test()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-pcc.sh:750:main() &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The reason is that we set the hsm-root wrong during copytool setup.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
